\par Starts with 1 point.
\par It is a very simple problem, but if someone disregards it, later when the level of the lectures are going up he might have difficulties.
\par
\par Don't underestimate it, study hard from the beginning.
\par
\par How many points is \b A\b0  worth?
\par
\par
\par }
