Dia. 04 If White Plays
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Let's check what happens if White plays first.
\par White takes the one stone with 1. By how many points White has increased his territory?
\par
\par You should add one captured stone and one point so White territory has increased by \cf1\b 2 points\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
