Dia. 05 If Black plays
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If it is Black's turn, Black saves his one stone with 1.
\par Like this Black's territory hasn't increased.
\par So only White's territory has increased in\b  Dia. 04\b0  by two points.
\par
\par That means White 1 in \b Dia. 04 \b0 and Black 1 in this diagram \cf1\b worth 2 points\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par }
